{"tid":1285963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下個大型活動 - 差你一個差好多","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T17:48:33.000Z","uid":274146,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e494136e7796714b943f707b65f525bb79a045c","tid":1285963,"uid":274146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"71之後好似無哂希望, 明明犧牲左咁多, 到頭來林鄭都係Don't give a shit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈來愈望唔到希望, 咁只會有愈多人<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死</span></span>。<br />\n雖然7月7日有活動, 但活動唔可以俾佢停！<br />\n我地需要下一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大型活動</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">活動反思:</span><br />\n點解林鄭唔理一百萬、二百萬人遊行? 唔理有人以死明志? <br />\n<del>因為你地係佢眼中根本唔重要呀!</del><br />\n要令林鄭理你地, 就要<span style=\"color: red;\">有份量既人</span>向佢施壓!<br />\n往後活動人數非常重要, 唔好再諗咩輕唔輕生, 差你一個真係差好多!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第一波 &ndash; 支持中銀活動</strong></span><br />\n目標: 感化 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中國銀行</span></span> 要求政府回應訴求<br />\n活動重點: 需要已經返工既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">青年&amp;中年人</span></strong>請假/罷工同用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你既錢</strong></span>支持活動<br />\n活動內容:<br />\n1. 眼見近期中銀同業拆息上升, 中銀肯定好唔夠錢洗。需要大家<span style=\"color: red;\">同一日同一時間</span>去中銀櫃員機入錢, 同時感召所有廢中廢老一齊加入。<br />\n2. 存完去銀行再存過, 戰線可以交換。事關每人存錢撳錢有上限, 睇返歷史行動派真係少之又少, 要死不如過黎行動, <span style=\"color: red;\">差你一個差好多</span><br />\n註: 提提大家唔好搞錯<span style=\"color: red;\">提款機</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">存款機</span>, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入錢變撳錢</span></span>, 櫃員機平時最多會放2,30萬, 而每部最多唔超過<span style=\"color: red;\">100萬</span>, 廢中廢老見到櫃員機無錢撳就大獲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第二波 &ndash; 紅隧灣仔運動場運動會</strong></span><br />\n目標: 感化 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">商界</span></span> 要求政府回應訴求<br />\n活動重點: Be Water, 東西紅隧都可以, 香港缺一不可<br />\n活動內容: <br />\n(1) <span style=\"color: red;\">紅隧係香港最繁忙既道路</span>。龍和道可以塞可以封, 紅隧一定唔得。去<span style=\"color: red;\">紅隧</span>附近灣仔運動場踢波, 如果要入紅隧執波, 搵多幾個fd一齊都好合理丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(2) 警方隨時會短期內以武力清場。Be Water, 即時散band轉往西隧/東隧再踢過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第三波 &ndash; 宣揚香港自由精神, 感化中國同胞</strong></span><br />\n目標: 感化 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">習近平</span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\">命令</span>政府回應訴求<br />\n活動重點:向中國同胞宣揚<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭</span></strong>既重要, 為中共未來民主社會播種<br />\n活動內容: <br />\n(1) 以各大平台, 任何媒體向中國同胞宣揚<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭</span>理念。事關中國人各家自掃門前雪, 重點唔在香港, 重點在於<span style=\"color: red;\">鼓勵被欺壓被迫害既中國人一齊企出黎, 對抗各個地方既霸權</span>。<br />\n(2) 加強死線既重要性, 唔好再係死線過好耐先做野。事前準備大量文宣圖片文字, 時機一到, 即刻開始瘋狂轟炸內地所有平台(e.g. 微信, 百度, 各直播平台)<br />\n註: 武漢事件中共極不願意重演, 需要教識內地同胞和平<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭</span>既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n死線仍然非常重要, 必須再次設死線要求林鄭回應訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次死線建議: <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">7月18日夜晚10點</span></span><br />\n(死線一過即時中國文宣開始 -&gt; 719支持中銀 -&gt; 719中午灣仔運動場會合)<br />\n原因: <br />\n1. 71之後需要時間回氣, 同時預留充足時間文宣同準備, 就算你連登入面幾多人推都係圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 要大大力向社會各界宣傳。 <br />\n2. 活動間隔不宜過長, 熱度只會減退, 就算有人死親身有遊行過, 香港人都係咁善忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 7月19日星期五適合連帶星期六日後續活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係發夢有人報夢我知, 活動好粗疏, 務求拋磚引玉, 大家再諗下點樣救救香港。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以失望，不要絕望。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"496270e2d5c3e5b205b87f2b3f206ac7a7546b12","tid":1285963,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:40:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a173c4b42e8549bc27506afd1a4f259c5a463c2","tid":1285963,"uid":147366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:42:38.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"fc83ec41ab817454cda85a374a6211032263598f","tid":1285963,"uid":195493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"去中銀入錢？下？唔get喎"},{"pid":"acd10e57e660f56e92533b30df5aa60f8bb7ddeb","tid":1285963,"uid":39258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc83ec41ab817454cda85a374a6211032263598f","tid":1285963,"uid":195493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"去中銀入錢？下？唔get喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"咩入錢，呢個巴係咪藍曲緊"},{"pid":"35c5b6704e01aae0ff268714fa256e14455cbf13","tid":1285963,"uid":39258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:47:12.000Z","msg":"ban"},{"pid":"afd469cf38e5474488b53146c25263cbbfb55672","tid":1285963,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xA3w1s1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxA3w1s1.png&h=22d8bfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF0LiCS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF0LiCS.png&h=986b6f5e&s